<h2 class="chapter">3 Installation</h2>

<p>Installing Octave.app is easy. Just drag the Octave.app icon from the <span class="file">octave.dmg</span> to another place of your filesystem (eg. to your desktop or even better to your applications folder) and that's it, you're done. Double&ndash;click the Octave.app to start up Octave. <br> <br>
This does not installed any further files elsewhere in your filesystem. To remove it, just drag the Octave.app icon to the Trash.  If you're new to Octave then you may have a look at the documents that come with your Octave. These <span class="file">*.pdf</span> files are installed in the docs folder of your <span class="file">octave.dmg</span> file.

